text: Félicité Louise Henriette "Fé" Sciarone (12 August 1922 - 8 April 2014) was a Dutch radio actress and comedienne. Her best known appearances include Dood in de jungle (1955), Een merkwaardig geval van zielsverhuizing (1969), De generaal (1976), Dit is uw kans (1979) and Vijf gemaskerde mannen (1982). She started her career in 1950 and retired in 1984. She was born in The Hague, South Holland. In 1959 she voiced Maleficient in the first Dutch translation of Sleeping Beauty from Walt Disney. Sciarone died on 8 April 2014 in Amsterdam, North Holland, aged 91.Death notice in NRC Handelsblad on 16 April 2014 ==References== ==Other websites== * Fé Sciarone at Radiopedia Category:1922 births Category:2014 deaths Category:Dutch comedians Category:Actors from The Hague Category:Radio actors
